{"type": "article", "id": 5041, "title": "3D 打印固件连接器Keystones", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-08T08:04:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233635qwcUCrEnh5Jguk1z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t来自于荷兰鹿特丹的设计工作室 Minale-Maeda 去年带来他一款他们设计的 3D 打印固件连接器Keystones ，专门为板材类家具而设计。在用户自行组装家具时，不用任何的螺丝钉或者胶黏剂，只需将家具的各部件固定在 Keystones 里即可，而且如果家里有 3D 打印机的话，在家里就可以将这些固件连接器在线打印出来，同时也简化了拆卸家具的步骤与方法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233633lfR1WNSD84IubeKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052336331EnIDSKz2AmZtj5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233634XvoV9mub6yAxrsHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233634DnBx15lHO7YfymZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}